# Next.js App Router Rules

## app/page.tsx
Follow Next.js App Router conventions. Ensure default exports for server components where applicable.

## app/layout.tsx
Use RootLayout correctly to structure the main page layout, navigation, and footer. Add proper html/body wrappers and metadata.

## app/globals.css
Maintain the neobrutalist + futurist fintech + cyberpunk style. Ensure styling works smoothly across all pages. Reuse global css without adding heavy dependencies.

## Client Component Rules
Use `"use client"` directive strictly only when React hooks (useState, useEffect) or browser APIs are required. Default to server components.

## Metadata Rules
Use Next.js Metadata API for titles, descriptions, open graph settings, and canonical URLs. All open graph and canonical URLs must use the absolute domain https://smb-ai-builder.vercel.app.
